					"type": 23,
					"value": "Voicebark played by Wyll when he enters Blushing Mermaid: this place has historical importance to him, he smooched some ladies.\r\n\r\nIMPORTANT: The answer node may not play in case there are no fitting players to answer Wyll, so it should still make sense even without an answer."
